### ========================================
### Calendar API Tests with the REST Client Extension
### ========================================

### ----------------------------------------
### 0. JWT Token holen
### ----------------------------------------

# @name login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/jwt/create/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dev@dev.de",
  "password": "dev"
}

###

@token = {{login.response.body.access}}

### ----------------------------------------
### 1. Events abrufen
### ----------------------------------------

### Alle Events (Standard-Zeitraum)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calendar/events/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Events mit Zeitraum
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calendar/events/?start_date=2026-02-01&end_date=2026-05-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Events mit erzwungenem CalDAV-Sync
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calendar/events/?start_date=2026-02-01&end_date=2026-05-31&force_sync=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ----------------------------------------
### 2. Event erstellen
### ----------------------------------------

### Normales Event erstellen
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calendar/events/create/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Team-Meeting",
  "description": "Wöchentliches Standup",
  "start_date": "2026-03-02T10:00:00Z",
  "end_date": "2026-03-02T11:00:00Z",
  "location": "Büro",
  "all_day": false
}

###

### Ganztages-Event erstellen
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calendar/events/create/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Betriebsausflug",
  "description": "Jährlicher Ausflug",
  "start_date": "2026-04-15T00:00:00Z",
  "end_date": "2026-04-16T00:00:00Z",
  "all_day": true
}

###

### Event mit URL erstellen
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calendar/events/create/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Video-Call",
  "start_date": "2026-03-05T14:00:00Z",
  "end_date": "2026-03-05T15:00:00Z",
  "url": "https://meet.example.com/abc123"
}

###

### Nur Pflichtfelder (title, start_date, end_date)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calendar/events/create/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Kurzer Termin",
  "start_date": "2026-03-10T09:00:00Z",
  "end_date": "2026-03-10T09:30:00Z"
}

###

### end_date vor start_date (sollte 400 zurückgeben)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calendar/events/create/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Ungültiges Event",
  "start_date": "2026-03-10T12:00:00Z",
  "end_date": "2026-03-10T11:00:00Z"
}

###

### Ohne Titel (sollte 400 zurückgeben)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calendar/events/create/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "start_date": "2026-03-10T09:00:00Z",
  "end_date": "2026-03-10T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### Ungültige URL (sollte 400 zurückgeben)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calendar/events/create/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Event mit falscher URL",
  "start_date": "2026-03-10T09:00:00Z",
  "end_date": "2026-03-10T10:00:00Z",
  "url": "keine-url"
}

###

### Leerer Body (sollte 400 zurückgeben)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calendar/events/create/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{}

###

### ----------------------------------------
### 3. Event aktualisieren
### ----------------------------------------

### Event aktualisieren (UID anpassen!)
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calendar/events/DEINE-EVENT-UID-HIER/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Team-Meeting (aktualisiert)",
  "description": "Neuer Raum",
  "start_date": "2026-03-02T10:30:00Z",
  "end_date": "2026-03-02T11:30:00Z",
  "location": "Konferenzraum B"
}

###

### Ungültige Daten beim Update (sollte 400 zurückgeben)
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calendar/events/DEINE-EVENT-UID-HIER/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Update ohne Zeiten"
}

###

### ----------------------------------------
### 4. Event löschen
### ----------------------------------------

### Event löschen (UID anpassen!)
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calendar/events/DEINE-EVENT-UID-HIER/delete/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Nicht existierendes Event löschen (sollte 404 zurückgeben)
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/calendar/events/nicht-existierende-uid/delete/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
